reviewText:
The package came in perfect shape. It was cutely wrapped up in gift wrap and the candy assortment that came with the dvd box set was so cool. We love British TV and the added bonus of some Brit candy was very neat. I had the shipping arrival date to be somewhere between May 31- July 7 and it arrived the last week of May, so I was very pleased that it came so quickly.
Thanks so much :)
